videos.description: Ty Jerome finds Jack Salt under the basket who puts in a tough layup.
videos.headline: Virginia's ball movement leads to Salt layup

videos.description: Good passing by the Yellow Jackets leads to a Tadric Jackson 3-pointer that puts them up in the first half against No. 1 Virginia.
videos.headline: Jackson puts Georgia Tech up early

videos.description: Mamadi Diakite hits a jumper in the key while drawing a foul to set up a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Diakite uses sweet move to get bucket

videos.description: Mamadi Diakite throws down a two-handed slam off a nice pass from De'Andre Hunter and pumps up the Cavaliers.
videos.headline: Diakite's jam hypes up Virginia's bench
